show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: A story of a man who is dumped, humiliated, and left for dead, only to be granted cursed power by a mysterious sage. He returns stronger and deadlier, unrecognizable to those who previously wronged him, now possessing the power of the "Strongest Curse Master". Watch Now!
